&lt;li&gt;Operate key parts of a sophisticated data analysis pipeline&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor and troubleshoot production jobs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor and work through list of data-related issues raised by the system, drilling into those requiring action, including looking into the code&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consult with developers to determine appropriate courses of action and make suggestions for improvements to the system&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor support channels and respond to user issues (2-10 per day)&lt;/li&gt;
